{"tid":2068900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反修例一年】被捕示威者棄保流亡海外尋政治庇護無期","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T05:33:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b78a732f93221f850b8360f10e19a02e31d39e56","tid":2068900,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/反修例-年-被捕示威者棄保流亡海外尋政治庇護無期-012041999.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E5%B9%B4-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%A3%84%E4%BF%9D%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E5%B0%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7%E7%84%A1%E6%9C%9F-012041999.html&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=d54950a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/反修例-年-被捕示威者棄保流亡海外尋政治庇護無期-012041999.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】反修例事件一周年，在前線參與示威的年輕人部分決定到海外申請政治庇護，他們在外地面對甚麼困難呢？<br />\n<br />\n化名PE仔曾是前線示威者，去年十一月理工大學發生激烈的警民衝突，PE仔在事件中被捕，被控暴動罪，今年年初決定棄保到澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n離鄉別井，政治庇護的審批遙遙無期，她表示生活並非想像般容易適應。<br />\n<br />\n這班網上商店經營者，正協助好像PE仔一班在海外的年輕人。除了提供財政支援外，又組織海外港人接濟他們。<br />\n<br />\n根據協助他們的團體估計，較多人選擇去台灣、加拿大及澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n去年反修例運動至今，警方拘捕接近9000人，至於有幾多人棄保離開香港，警方就表示沒有相關的數字。"},{"pid":"4e442626a7d9193eb2473eb853728fef36503411","tid":2068900,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ada91e874866b6bc17a2486a5e8f75c85bcb7e","tid":2068900,"uid":216776,"like":5,"dislike":18,"score":-13,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"成世人就咁玩完<img src=\"/assets/fa